cess.\n\n3. **Subquery Optimization**: The query uses `EXISTS` and `NOT EXISTS` subqueries. Optimizing these subqueries can improve performance.\n\n   - **Rule: JOIN_SUB_QUERY_TO_CORRELATE**: This rule converts sub-queries from join expressions into Correlate instances. This transformation can optimize the execution of subqueries by leveraging correlated subqueries.\n\n4. **Aggregate Optimization**: The query performs aggregation with a `GROUP BY` clause. Optimizing this aggregation can improve performance.\n\n   - **Rule: AGGREGATE_FILTER_TRANSPOSE**: This rule transposes an aggregate on a filter, pushing the aggregate below the filter. This can help in reducing the data size before aggregation, thus optimizing the aggregation process.\n\n5. **Sort Optimization**: The query includes an `ORDER BY` clause. Optimizing the sort operation can improve performance.\n\n   - **Rule: SORT_REMOVE**: If the input to the sort operation is already sorted, this rule can remove the sort operation. However, in this case, the sort is necessary for the `ORDER BY` clause, so this rule may not be applicable.\n\nAfter considering the above rules, we can apply the following sequence of rules to optimize the query:\n\n```python\n[\n    "FILTER_INTO_JOIN",\n    "JOIN_CONDITION_PUSH",\n    "JOIN_SUB_QUERY_TO_CORRELATE",\n    "AGGREGATE_FILTER_TRANSPOSE"\n]\n```\n\n### Optimized Query Transformation:\n\n1. **Apply FILTER_INTO_JOIN**: Push filter conditions into join conditions to reduce data size before joins.\n\n2. **Apply JOIN_CONDITION_PUSH**: Push join predicates into the inputs of the join to further reduce data size before the join operation.\n\n3. **Apply JOIN_SUB_QUERY_TO_CORRELATE**: Convert subqueries into Correlate instances to optimize subquery execution.\n\n4. **Apply AGGREGATE_FILTER_TRANSPOSE**: Transpose the aggregate operation below the filter to reduce data size before aggregation.\n\nBy applying these rules, the query execution plan can be optimized to process less data at each stage, leading to improved performance.', 'time': 6.484618425369263}
